PrecisRe-appointment of TONY MANGLAVITI, of Dollard-des-Ormeaux, Quebec, FARID OSMANE, of Laval-ouest, Quebec, and HÉLÈNE PANAGAKOS, of Montreal, Quebec, as full-time members of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective April 20, 2001.
